# Save to Spotify library

After ranking, `RankComplete` shows the final list and **Save to Spotify library**.

## API (batch size 50)

- Tracks: `PUT /v1/me/tracks?ids=`
- Albums: `PUT /v1/me/albums?ids=`
- Artists: `PUT /v1/me/following?type=artist&ids=`

Implement in `spotifyLibrary.ts`; chunk with `helpers/chunkIds.ts`.

## Scopes

`user-library-modify`, `user-follow-modify` (+ existing auth scopes in `spotifyAuth.ts`).

403 → user must reconnect with updated Dashboard scopes.

## Types

`RankedItem` in `apiTypes/rankedItem.ts`. Prefer track-only ranking; expand albums/artists to tracks before rank when saving order matters. Mixed lists: `saveRankedToLibrary` walks rank order.

## UX

Progress `Saving n/total`, success/partial failure, mock via `VITE_SPOTIFY_MOCK`.

See `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` for full flow.
